WEBVTT

00:03:58.506 --> 00:04:00.585
I felt backed into a corner.

00:04:01.176 --> 00:04:04.600
My head and my heart
were in conflict with each other,

00:04:04.624 --> 00:04:06.759
and the thought of the death penalty

00:04:06.783 --> 00:04:08.279
made me sick.

00:04:11.369 --> 00:04:16.148
However, following
the judge's instructions,

00:04:16.172 --> 00:04:18.574
being a law-abiding person,

00:04:19.972 --> 00:04:21.268
I gave up.

00:04:22.390 --> 00:04:26.678
I gave up and voted along
with the other 11 jurors.

